 Megastrom looked at his scanners. "Finally. Our #1 foot soilder  has 
arrived." A small transport pod landed outside the destron ship. Out stepped 
god neptune. His beast mode is formed by three ancient dinosaurs. Scylle, 
Coelagon, Terrormandar and Seaphantom. Two are shark bot beast modes. Scylle 
is a stinger.(depth charge beast mode.) and collagon is a seal looking beast 
mode.. They barley ever parted. When they where togeather they formwed ethier 
the monster beast mode. Or the robot mode known as God Neptune. His Ring 
sword was his main weapon. He was 7 feet tall and had shoulder cannons and a 
energy disc shooting hole on his chest. He walked up to the base. He called 
out. "I wish entrance."
